<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Project Prototype - Sustainable Consumption</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-success shadow-sm">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Sustainable Consumption</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#mission">Mission</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#problem">Problem</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#awareness">Awareness</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#consumers">Consumers</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/crossword">Crossword Puzzle</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/quiz">Quiz</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="text-center p-5 bg-light shadow-sm">
        <h1 class="display-4">Sustainable Consumption</h1>
        <p class="lead">Join us in promoting sustainable practices for a better world.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="welcome-message">
        Welcome, <strong><%= user %></strong>
    </div>
    <div id="account-actions" class="text-center my-4">
        <form action="/delete-account" method="POST" class="d-inline">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Delete Account</button>
        </form>
        <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-secondary">Logout</a>
    </div>

    <main class="container">
        <section id="mission" class="my-5 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-success">Our Mission</h2>
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <p class="fs-5">Promoting resource efficiency, reducing waste, and encouraging sustainable practices across all levels of production and consumption.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="/img/2.jpg" alt="Sustainability" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="problem" class="my-5 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-success">The Problem</h2>
            <p class="fs-5">Everything is standardized to reduce costs and programmed to be obsolete, exacerbating global inequalities and limiting access to resources for marginalized groups.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="awareness" class="my-5 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-success">Raise Awareness</h2>
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="/img/11.jpg" alt="Awareness" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <p class="fs-5">We aim to raise awareness and inspire more thoughtful consumption behaviors. Redefining our habits is key to building a sustainable future.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="consumers" class="my-5 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-success">What Can We Do as Consumers</h2>
            <ul class="list-unstyled fs-5">
                <li>✔ Choose sustainable products</li>
                <li>✔ Support local and ethical brands</li>
                <li>✔ Buy less, buy better</li>
                <li>✔ Educate yourself and others</li>
                <li>✔ Be mindful of resource consumption</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="resources" class="our-resources my-5">
            <h2 class="text-success text-center mb-4">Resources for Sustainable Consumption</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title text-success">Sustainability Guide</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">A comprehensive guide to living a more sustainable lifestyle.</p>
                            <a href="https://sustainabilityguide.eu/guides/" class="btn btn-success">Read More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title text-success">Local Ethical Brands</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Discover local brands committed to ethical practices and sustainability.</p>
                            <a href="https://www.thegoodtrade.com/features/fair-trade-clothing/" class="btn btn-success">Explore Brands</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title text-success">Reduce, Reuse, Recycle</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Learn how to reduce waste through effective recycling and reuse strategies.</p>
                            <a href="https://www.epa.gov/recycle" class="btn btn-success">Learn More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-success text-white text-center p-3 mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Sustainable Consumption Project - All rights reserved.</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-white text-decoration-none">Privacy Policy</a> | 
            <a href="#" class="text-white text-decoration-none">Terms of Service</a>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/delete-account.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

